Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">尋找黑警性暴力證人/受害者，協助國際遊說</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2640629789347426%26id%3D124616407615456&d=%2BaoNGjxKkOyNIKnkVXg3cTk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=2f73b6cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2640629789347426&amp;id=124616407615456</a><br />\n<br />\nPost：<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eDEkrT\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eDEkrT</a><br />\n<br />\n//平等機會婦女聯席發言人區美寶稱，3個組織11月初共同發起控訴警察性暴力的國際聯署，截至本月7日收集到21國共85個團體聯署支持。為了向聯合國專家展開更有力游說，3個組織呼籲受害者主動聯絡他們並接受訪談，強調會保密。//<br />\n<br />\n我們現正收集抗爭者在抗爭期間／被捕後遭受警察性暴力對待的資料，作以下用途：<br />\n1. 協助受害人可以完整保留該事件之紀錄<br />\n2. 整理資料並製成 #ProtestToo 實錄，以作追究之用<br />\n3. 收集國際聯署（進行中），結合個案提交聯合國，爭取國際間關注及支持<br />\n4. 要求香港政府獨立、公正地徹查「反送中運動」發生的性暴力<br />\n<br />\n*個人資料及通訊紀錄在實錄完成後可按受訪者意願全部銷毀<br />\n詳情及相關安排請聯絡Tg @protesttoo"},{"pid":"e96f15833f6ec913953c0de8a3a7a4f73f39f284","tid":1777573,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96c390aaa5037541af50fda5e409c8812dc2d098","tid":1777573,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10381d749b28491f2cf6e398bb7e575d1f1e8e07","tid":1777573,"uid":181088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:09:16.000Z","msg":"小英今鋪仆街啦⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:19:19.000Z","msg":"邊有可能輸 韓國佬得1x%支持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T10:49:45.000Z","msg":"燒山死都燈都返生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023766ef4703613925ff2c9c08b6b4233920f2a2","tid":1777573,"uid":302348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f37f41d7b958af32cb1297f63606bc45fdb99dd","tid":1777573,"uid":52658,"like":0,"